---
import { CardWrapper, Tooltip } from '@components';
---

<section class="container">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <CardWrapper class="card | flow" hasBorder data-type="twitch">
      <div class="flow">
        <img src="/svg/twitch.svg" alt="logo twitch" class="twitch" />
        <h3 class="card__title">Streamer en twitch</h3>
        <p class="card__paragraph">
          He descubierto que ser streamer e interactuar con mi comunidad es divertido y me ha
          permitido crecer aún mas como profesional
        </p>
      </div>

      <picture class="twitch-img">
        <source srcset="/assets/images/ana-2.avif" type="image/avif" />
        <source srcset="/assets/images/ana-2.webp" type="image/webp" />
        <img
          src="/assets/images/ana-2.webp"
          alt="Ana foto audifonos"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          fetchpriority="low"
        />
      </picture>
    </CardWrapper>

    <CardWrapper class="card | flow" hasBorder data-type="ux-engineer">
      <h3 class="card__title">UX engineer</h3>
      <p class="card__paragraph">
        Hoy en día estoy buscando adquirir mas habilidades, y manejas lenguajes de programación ha
        sido una excelente forma de mejorar en mi área de UX
      </p>
      <div class="hobbies-imgs-group">
        <Tooltip message="HTML 5"><img src="/svg/html-logo.svg" alt="logo html" /></Tooltip>
        <Tooltip message="CSS 3"><img src="/svg/css-logo.svg" alt="logo css" /></Tooltip>
        <Tooltip message="Astro"><img src="/svg/astro-logo.svg" alt="logo astro" /></Tooltip>
        <Tooltip message="JavaScript"><img src="/svg/js-logo.svg" alt="logo javascript" /></Tooltip>
        <Tooltip message="React"><img src="/svg/react-logo.svg" alt="logo react" /></Tooltip>
        <Tooltip message="GitHub"><img src="/svg/github-logo.svg" alt="logo github" /></Tooltip>
      </div>
    </CardWrapper>

    <CardWrapper hasBorder class="card" data-type="volunteering">
      <div class="flow">
        <h3 class="card__title">Voluntariado</h3>
        <p class="card__paragraph">
          Ser voluntaria me ha dado muchas oportunidades laborales y conocer excelentes
          profesionales, adicional aporto desde mis habilidades de diseño a comunidades de
          tecnología, dándome tambien experiencia en organización de eventos y conferencias como la <span
            >JSconf 2024</span
          >, hackathons, siendo charlista, contribuyendo al open source y más, es una manera de
          regresarle a la comunidad todo lo que he aprendido y transmitirlo a nuevas generaciones.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="events-container">
        <div class="event" data-name="js-chile">
          <img
            src="/svg/jschile.svg"
            alt="Javascript Chile"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
          />
          <p>Javascript Chile</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event" data-name="spark-code">
          <img
            src="/svg/sparkcode.svg"
            alt="Spark Code"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
          />
          <p>Spark code</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event" data-name="jsconf-chile">
          <img
            src="/svg/jsconf.svg"
            alt="JS Conf Chile"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
          />
          <p>Js Conf Chile 2024</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event" data-name="women-techmakers">
          <img
            src="/svg/wtm.svg"
            alt="Women Techmakers"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
          />
          <p>Women Techmakers Chile</p>
        </div>
        <div class="event" data-name="js-venezuela">
          <img
            src="/svg/jsvzla.svg"
            alt="Javascript Venezuela"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
          />
          <p>Javascript Venezuela</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </CardWrapper>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wrapper {
    display: grid;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    margin-inline: 1rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-items: center;
  }

  .card {
    --flow-spacer: 1.4375rem;

    background-color: hsl(240, 4%, 5%);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 0.0625rem solid hsl(0, 0%, 16%);
    padding: 2.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    .card__title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 2.375rem;
      color: hsl(300, 14%, 97%);
    }

    .card__paragraph {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5rem;
      color: hsl(236, 25%, 75%);
    }

    &[data-type='twitch'] {
      .twitch {
        position: relative;
        inline-size: 2.5rem;
        top: 0.3125rem;
      }

      .twitch-img {
        img {
          inline-size: 100%;
          border-radius: 1.5rem;
          object-fit: cover;
          object-position: 20% 10%;

          @media (width >= 1200px) {
            max-block-size: 26.0625rem;
          }
        }
      }

      @media (min-width: 600px) and (max-width: 1200px) {
        flex-direction: row;
        gap: 2rem;

        img {
          max-block-size: 40rem;
        }
      }
    }

    .hobbies-imgs-group {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2.25rem;

      @media (width <= 600px) {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      img {
        inline-size: 100%;
        max-inline-size: 5rem;
      }
    }
  }

  .card[data-type='volunteering'] {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 2.25rem;
    inline-size: 100%;

    @media (width >= 650px) {
      diplay: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    span {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
    }

    .events-container {
      block-size: 18.75rem;
      inline-size: 100%;
      max-inline-size: 17.625rem;
      position: relative;

      .event {
        display: flex;
        position: absolute;
        inline-size: fit-content;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.375rem;

        p {
          inline-size: max-content;
          font-weight: 600;
          font-size: 0.625rem;
          line-height: 0.5625rem;
          padding: 0.1875rem 0.2813rem;
          border-radius: 1.25rem;
        }
        p::after {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          left: -10%;
          bottom: 30%;

          inline-size: 100%;
          block-size: 100%;
          max-inline-size: 1.0625rem;
          max-block-size: 1.25rem;

          transform: translateX(-50%);
          clip-path: polygon(50% 85%, 0 100%, 50% 0, 100% 100%);
          rotate: -35deg;
        }

        &[data-name='js-chile'] {
          p {
            background-color: hsl(53, 93%, 54%);
            color: hsl(240, 4%, 5%);
          }
          p::after {
            background-color: hsl(53, 93%, 54%);
          }
        }

        &[data-name='spark-code'] {
          top: 65%;
          left: 9%;
          p {
            background-color: hsl(287, 68%, 60%);
          }

          p::after {
            background-color: hsl(287, 68%, 60%);
          }
        }

        &[data-name='jsconf-chile'] {
          top: 25%;
          left: 25%;
          p {
            background-color: hsl(53, 67%, 60%);
            color: hsl(0, 0%, 0%);
          }

          p::after {
            background-color: hsl(53, 67%, 60%);
          }
        }

        &[data-name='women-techmakers'] {
          top: 5%;
          left: 70%;
          p {
            background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
            color: hsl(0, 0%, 0%);
            max-inline-size: 6.5625rem;
            text-align: center;
          }

          p::after {
            background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
          }
        }

        &[data-name='js-venezuela'] {
          top: 55%;
          left: 65%;

          p {
            border: 1px solid hsl(53, 93%, 54%);
            color: hsl(53, 93%, 54%);
          }

          p::after {
            background-color: hsl(53, 93%, 54%);
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (width >= 1200px) {
    .wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      justify-items: start;
    }
    .card {
      .card__title {
        line-height: 3rem;
      }

      &[data-type='twitch'] {
        grid-row: 1 / 3;

        .twitch-img {
          max-block-size: 29.8125rem;
        }
      }

      &[data-type='ux-engineer'],
      &[data-type='volunteering'] {
        grid-column: span 2;
      }

      &[data-type='ux-engineer'] {
        .card__paragraph {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          line-height: 2.25rem;
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
